cs.RO, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV

The paper deals with multi-robot teams and proposes tracking strategies for ground robots to follow aerial robots while maintaining connectivity. This falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The paper also addresses the issue of connectivity maintenance, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY). The proposed strategies involve density functions and virtual limits, which are techniques used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) respectively.
